long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tabs a mess? 99 things open but none are what you're looking for? Give Tab Search a try. Just type 'tab' and a guess as to the name or url of the tab you're looking for into the omnibar and automagically be taken to that tab.
